19:06.160 --> 19:10.280
-They need to test everything because--
-Can you-- I've just had a heart attack!

19:10.360 --> 19:12.600
-Stop making me stressed!
-Calm down.

19:12.680 --> 19:16.160
Calm down? If I have another one,
it'll be your fault.

19:16.240 --> 19:17.160
How dare you, madam?

19:18.080 --> 19:21.080
-Have you not got somewhere else to be?
-I have, actually.

19:21.160 --> 19:23.640
-Great.
-I'm going out for a drink.

19:23.720 --> 19:26.600
I can still do that.
I've got a good heart. I can enjoy myself.

19:26.680 --> 19:27.920
Okay. See you tomorrow.

19:28.000 --> 19:30.480
-Hopefully not.
-Wow. Don't say that.

19:33.120 --> 19:34.160
See you later.

19:45.920 --> 19:47.120
You look down, boy.

19:48.760 --> 19:49.600
Yeah.

19:50.720 --> 19:53.400
Need some advice
from a dude who's been there, done that?

19:55.840 --> 20:00.200
I'm not gonna make it in showbiz.
It just doesn't happen to people like me.

20:00.280 --> 20:01.720
-Fat people?
-No!

20:02.560 --> 20:05.240
I mean ordinary people
who live in small towns

20:05.320 --> 20:07.960
with the worst agent in the world
whose idea of a big break

20:08.040 --> 20:10.440
is pretending to be disabled
on a reality show.

20:10.960 --> 20:12.520
I think you might be right, mate.

20:13.040 --> 20:13.960
