20:14.920 --> 20:17.600
-Wish I was wrong in this case.
-Ah, spot on, son.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.120
Who cares anyway?

20:20.680 --> 20:21.760
Huh?

20:21.840 --> 20:23.600
Got everything you need right here.

20:24.120 --> 20:25.560
Tambury's a lovely town.

20:26.280 --> 20:27.400
Hmm?

20:27.480 --> 20:28.840
Easy job. Nice mum.

20:29.640 --> 20:32.080
-Great friend. You.
-Back at you, boy.

20:33.400 --> 20:35.240
Come on. Come on.

20:36.600 --> 20:38.360
Why do you wanna be a fake wannabe anyway?

20:39.320 --> 20:40.160
