22:16.440 --> 22:18.760
-No! Sorry, did that sound a bit pathetic?

22:18.840 --> 22:20.480
No. It's funny.

22:20.560 --> 22:23.800
I'm always the one who does the overtime,
who covers for everybody's holidays

22:23.880 --> 22:27.120
